data.title: Novato Location Map & Directions
data.text:
Novato Office and Laser Vision Correction Center

165 Rowland Way (NCH Medical Office Building), Suite 207, Novato, CA 94945

(415) 892-0111

Hours: 8:00 a.m. to 5:00 p.m.

Monday through Friday

From 101 southbound, exit at “Rowland Boulevard.” Go left, over the freeway, to Rowland Way. Turn left onto Rowland Way and follow this road to the end. Novato Community Hospital and the Medical Office building are located here. Enter the Medical Office Building and take the elevator to the second floor, Suite 207.

Coming north on 101, exit at “Rowland Boulevard.” Turn right then immediately left onto Rowland Way. Follow this road to the end. Novato Community Hospital and the Medical Office building are located here. Enter the Medical Office Building and take the elevator to the second floor. MarinEyes is located in Suite 207 of the office building.

Coming west on Highway 37, exit north on 101. Take the first exit, “Rowland Boulevard.” Turn right then immediately left onto Rowland Way. Follow this road to the end. Novato Community Hospital and the Medical Office building are located here. Enter the Medical Office Building and take the elevator to the second floor. MarinEyes is located in Suite 207 of the office building.
